http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Thiruvananthapuram/Job-fair-at-SCTCE/article13991375.ece

The Sree Chitra Thirunal College of Engineering (SCTCE), Pappanamcode, is conducted a job fair on the college premises on January 16 and 17.Being organised by the Career Guidance and Placement Unit of the college, the job fair will provide opportunities ranging from medical coding to web analytics for the participants.Employment opportunities in various sectors including Information Technology and the core fields have also been assured by the organisers.Further details on the job fair can be obtained by visiting the Facebook page of the SCTCE Job Fair 2016 or by calling on phone number 8138078400.